OL,3,CPlans submitted for a new crematorium
OL,5,FPlans have been submitted for a new
OL,6,Fcrematorium on a 3.4 hectare site.
OL,8,FThe single-storey structure will be
OL,9,Fsited on farmland approximately two
OL,10,Fmiles east of the village of
OL,11,FSmithfield, and eight miles north of
OL,12,FCarlisle.
OL,14,FI and K Enterprises Ltd submitted the
OL,15,Fproposals, which detail around 6,000
OL,16,Fsquare metres of landscaped grounds.
