OL,3,CPlans submitted for a new crematorium
OL,5,FThe grounds will include a formal
OL,6,Fremembrance garden suitable for the
OL,7,Fscattering of ashes, an informal
OL,8,Fstepped garden, a water fountain and
OL,9,Fpavilion, and 80 car parking spaces.
OL,11,FThe crematorium itself will measure
OL,12,F715 square metres and seat just over
OL,13,F100 people.
OL,15,FThe building will feature asymmetrical
OL,16,Froof forms, in a style described in
OL,17,Fplanning documents as "contemporary
OL,18,Fyet simplistic, relying on the use of
OL,19,Fhigh-quality materials".
