OL,3,CPlans submitted for a new crematorium
OL,5,FThese materials include bricks made of
OL,6,FSt Bees sandstone and Douglas Fir
OL,7,Ftimber structures.
OL,9,FThe site will be reached by a new
OL,10,Faccess road, constructed to come off
OL,11,Fthe A6071, and the plans promise to
OL,12,Fretain the historic milestone on this
OL,13,Froad.
OL,15,FThere are currently three crematoria
OL,16,Fwithin 60km of the proposed site:
OL,17,FCarlisle Crematorium, Roucan Loch
OL,18,FCrematorium, and Eden Valley
OL,19,FCrematorium.
