OL,3,CPlans submitted for a new crematorium
OL,5,FExplaining the need for another
OL,6,Fcrematorium, the plans state that "the
OL,7,Fcremation rate in the UK is at an all-
OL,8,Ftime high", and that "the proportions
OL,9,Fof cremations is projected to increase
OL,10,Fby approximately 2% every five years".
OL,12,FI and K Enterprises expects to conduct
OL,13,Faround 1,000 services a year at the
OL,14,Fsite, and the crematorium's opening
OL,15,Fhours are likely to be 10am-6pm on
OL,16,Fweekdays, and 10am-4pm on weekends.
